    "name": "The Legend of Heroes: Trails beyond the Horizon",
    "steam_appid": 3316940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The prophesied end of the Zemurian continent draws near, and so does the launch of humanity's first foray into space. A sudden invitation from Marduk to cooperate in a high-tech training exercise sets Van Arkride, Ashen Chevalier Rean Schwarzer, and Father Kevin Graham on a collision course with the secrets that lay at the very core of Zemuria.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their paths may diverge, but the ultimate question remains the same: Just what lies beyond the edge of the horizon?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316940/extras/b9e78688910a2056fe67a5d9f30a977e.avif?t=1771470581\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore detailed locations across the Calvard Republic, strengthen your connections with your allies, and uncover what lies beyond the horizon of Zemuria across three intertwining story paths. Plus, Trails beyond the Horizon introduces new gameplay mechanics to the beloved battle system introduced in Trails through Daybreak, giving you an unprecedented amount of options in both Field and Command Battles. Battle it out in the action-packed Field Battle mode, then swap to the turn-based Command Battle mode to strategically plan out your attacks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316940/extras/25af4b24a8e1798bff99a62ecbd2fdae.avif?t=1771470581\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New features include: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield more power in battle than ever before with <strong>Shard Commands</strong>! Utilize S-Boosts to give your party a range of benefits during battle. Each character and holo core comes with their own unique Shard Commands, so be sure to take advantage of them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Certain characters, such as Van with his ability to transform into the Grendel, can surge with extra strength using <strong>Awakening</strong> during Field Battles to temporarily increase their power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316940/extras/4d7ecd1f00affbb6d3ab77c67575875b.avif?t=1771470581\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of time itself with <strong>Z.O.C</strong>. to slow the speed of enemies to a crawl, allowing characters to perform multiple attacks in quick succession. Not only that, but while Z.O.C. is activated, your attack power and stun damage will dramatically increase, making stunning enemies with high defense a breeze! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plus, gather allies from all over Calvard and beyond and put a stop to Ouroboros' machinations in the <strong>Grim Garten</strong>, a dungeon that you can take on with your own custom party!</p>",
